Package: microweight
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Weighting Microdata Files
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Don",
           family = "Boyd",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "donboyd5@gmail.com")
Description: Tools for (1) splitting record weights for a microdata file across 
    states or other geographies in a manner that hits or comes close to targets 
    for those geographies, (2) for reweighting microdata files, and (3) for 
    selected other weighting tasks.
